text: Gong Guiping (born 1 February 1969) is a Chinese cross-country skier. She competed in four events at the 1992 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Chinese female cross- country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of China Category:Cross- country skiers at the 1992 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
